{"tid":788051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬來西亞總理馬哈蒂爾宣布取消東海岸鐵路計劃","createTime":"2018-08-21T07:29:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T10:34:52.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44df09b1fb7f90ca6117b3337793d78e202c898b","tid":788051,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:29:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1025721&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1025721%26csid%3D261_341&d=uDtCgsR86EXX3RESjWIgBv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=34e4da9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1025721&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬來西亞總理馬哈蒂爾結束訪華行程前召開記者會，宣布取消中資項目東海岸鐵路計劃及兩項油氣管道計劃。馬哈蒂爾指，由於國債問題，大馬政府現階段無力承擔，又指中國明白他們的問題，並同意取消項目，大馬當局會盡量減低賠償金額。<br />\n<br />\n馬哈蒂爾早前接受《財新網》訪問，提到大馬縮小或暫停涉及中資的項目，是因為政府無法負擔，與中國企業無關，他此行感受到中國理解大馬面臨的問題，相信兩國可以一起解決問題。"},{"pid":"9ba649cfb4ce7ff75e292b920fe07e0f784e0ead","tid":788051,"uid":10064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T07:33:57.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞早跳船早響受"},{"pid":"51c8397a75bd38937b7f6879aaac06d2022dfb01","tid":788051,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T10:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}